\pard\s5\sb240\sa120{\b\fs28 {\rtlch\f1 \b \fs28 Structural Elements\b0 }}\par
\pard\sa120 {\rtlch\f1 \fs24 Miscellaneous structural elements you can add to your document, like footnotes,}\par
\pard\sa120 {\rtlch\f1 \fs24 endnotes, dropcaps and the like.}\par
\pard\sa120 {\rtlch\f1 \b \fs26 Footnotes & Endnotes\b0 }\par
\pard\sa120 {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "#internal"}}{\fldrslt {\rtlch\f1 \fs24 Footnotes }}}{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "#internal"}}{\fldrslt {\rtlch\f1 \fs16 1 }}}{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "#internal"}}{\fldrslt {\rtlch\f1 \fs24 and endnotes }}}{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "#internal"}}{\fldrslt {\rtlch\f1 \fs16 i }}}{\rtlch\f1 \fs24 are automatically recognized and both are converted to}\par
\pard\sa120 {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "#internal"}}{\fldrslt {\rtlch\f1 \fs24 endnotes, with backlinks for maximum ease of use in ebook devices.}}}\par
\pard\sa120 {\rtlch\f1 \b \fs26 Dropcaps\b0 }\par
\pard\sa120 {\rtlch\f1 \fs24 rop caps are used to emphasize the leading paragraph at the start of a}\par
\pard\sa120 {\rtlch\f1 \fs24 section. In Word it is possible to specify how many lines of text a drop-cap}\par
\pard\s1\sb240\sa120{\b\fs44 {\rtlch\f1 \fs118 D }{\rtlch\f1 \fs24 should use.}}\par
\pard\sa120 {\rtlch\f1 \b \fs26 Links\b0 }\par
\pard\sa120 {\rtlch\f1 \fs24 Two kinds of links are possible, those that refer to an external website and those}\par
\pard\sa120 {\rtlch\f1 \fs24 that refer to locations inside the document itself. Both are supported by calibre. For}\par
\pard\sa120 {\rtlch\f1 \fs24 example, here is a link pointing to the }{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://calibre-ebook.com/download"}}{\fldrslt {\rtlch\f1 \fs24 calibre download page }}}{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://calibre-ebook.com/download"}}{\fldrslt {\rtlch\f1 \fs24 . Then we have a link that}}}\par
\pard\sa120 {\rtlch\f1 \fs24 points back to the section on }{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://calibre-ebook.com/download"}}{\fldrslt {\rtlch\f1 \fs24 paragraph level formatting }}}{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://calibre-ebook.com/download"}}{\fldrslt {\rtlch\f1 \fs24 in this document.}}}\par
