\pard\s5\sb240\sa120{\b\fs28 {\rtlch\f1 \b \fs28 Images\b0 }}\par
\pard\sa120 {\rtlch\f1 \fs24 Centered images like this are useful for large pictures that should be a focus of}\par
\pard\sa120 {\rtlch\f1 \fs24 attention.}\par
\pard\sa120 {\rtlch\f1 \fs24 There is no analogous technology in ebooks, so the conversion will usually end up}\par
\pard\sa120 {\rtlch\f1 \fs24 placing the image either centered or floating close to the point in the text where it}\par
\pard\sa120 {\rtlch\f1 \fs24 was }{\rtlch\f1 \i \fs24 inserted \i0 }{\rtlch\f1 \fs24 , not necessarily where it appears on the page in Word.}\par
